<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٥٨⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5532">غُنْدَرٌ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3384">عَبْدِ الرَّحْمَنِ بْنِ الْقَاسِمِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5159">أَبِيهِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3026">عَائِشَةَ </a>أَنَّهَا قَالَتْ <span class="c2">«مَا لِفَاطِمَةَ أَلَا تَتَّقِي اللهَ؟»</span> يَعْنِي: فِي قَوْلِهِ لَا سُكْنَى وَلَا نَفَقَةَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>